# ❓ Why use Path Compression?

Without path compression:

```text
Tree height can become large.
```

Path compression flattens the tree.

So future `find()` operations become very fast.

---

# ❓ Why use Union By Rank?

Union by rank ensures:

```text
Smaller tree attaches below larger tree.
```

This prevents skewed trees.

So operations remain efficient.

